'''Taseɣleyt''' d [[ameccaq]] imzirig ɣef tfekka tuwnist. Taseɣleyt d tin igan d taxatart s waṭas deg [[tanzeggit|tenzeggit]] yakk d [[tanezkeṛdist|tnezkeṛdist]].

== Taseɣleyt n twinest ==
Taseɣleyt n twinest d ameccaq ɣef twinest. Irem-a yettusexdem i wakken ad imel tifekkiwin timdettiyin. Akken i yettusexdem i wakken ad imel tifekkiwin tisnakanin timadwanin.

Taseɣleyt n twinest trennu s tmerniwt n wekdu-ines. Afaris n beṭṭu n tseɣleyt ɣef wekdu d usbiṭ, yerna s kra ɣef wuṭṭun 3, ayen yennumken d akken taseɣleyt tegda 3 n tikkal n wekdu.

=== Assaɣ yakk d Pi ===
Taseɣleyt n twinest yeqqen yakk d yiwet seg tmezgiwin tisnakanin tixatarin deg yakk taɣulin n [[tusnakt]], [[Pi]] (Azamul-is s Tegrikt '''π'''). Atig aneṭṭun n π yegda 3.14159... (ẓeṛ {{OEIS2C|id=A000796}}) yettwassen d afimudi gar n tseɣleyt d twinest ɣer wekdu-ines.
Tanfalit ɣef tseɣleyt n twinest tettili-d s wassaɣ<br />

<math>{C}=\pi\cdot{d}=2\pi\cdot{r}.\!</math> <br />

Anda '''C''' tesgensis taseɣleyt, ma d '''d''' yesgensis akdu n twinest, ma d '''r''' d [[aqqaṛ]]. 

